Say '''Sapi-an''' et kumapat ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Capiz]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 24,779 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 105.24 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumadwa ya distrito. Say zip code to et 5806.	
															
